title: Complete coverage: Wilson's Tyra Ott wins 3rd straight district tennis title
text:
By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 13, 2015 4:42 AM, updated October 13, 2015 4:53 AM View/Post Comments 
Wilson junior Tyra Ott made it a three-peat on Monday as she won her third consecutive District 11 Class AA title. 
She beat Notre Dame 's Coco Chen for the second straight year. This time around the final score was 6-3, 6-4.
